snippet.title: Akuto: Showdown PC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT MARCH 28, 2019 FOR WINDOWS, MAC, AND LINUX!!

Akuto: Showdown (previously known as Akuto: Mad World) is an award-nominated, isometric, fast-paced action game where players compete with swords and guns in intense versus matches.


BUY Akuto: Showdown right NOW:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/530130/Akuto_Showdown/
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/akuto-showdown
